    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_vm.00183.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Laurel Hills <choice><abbr>N.J.</abbr><expan>New Jersey</expan></choice></name>
                    <date when="1878-07-27">July 27th., 78.</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>My Dear, Dear, Friend,</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>I received the <choice><orig>rubarb</orig><reg>rhubarb</reg></choice> to-day, it came just in time:<ptr target="n0590"/> I have been sick for some time past, I took a dose of it as soon as I got it <gap reason="damage" extent="5 to 7 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> I was <gap reason="damage" extent="6 to 8 words" quantity="20" unit="chars"/> when <gap reason="damage" extent="6 to 8 words" quantity="20" unit="chars"/> and <gap reason="damage" extent="6 to 8 words" quantity="20" unit="chars"/> told <gap reason="damage" extent="6 to 8 words" quantity="20" unit="chars"/> on <gap reason="damage" extent="6 to 8 words" quantity="20" unit="chars"/> I look <gap reason="damage" extent="6 to 8 words" quantity="20" unit="chars"/> I did <gap reason="damage" extent="6 to 8 words" quantity="20" unit="chars"/> perhaps <gap reason="damage" extent="5 or 6 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> were <unclear reason="damage" cert="medium" resp="#vm">complaining</unclear> <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> up there.</p>                     
            
            <p>Mr. Whitman, I want to ask 
                
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc_vm.00184.jpg" type="verso"/>   
                
                <gap reason="damage" extent="3 words" quantity="15" unit="char"/> don't want 
                <gap reason="damage" extent="3 words" quantity="15" unit="char"/> at me, it is
                
                this&#8212;do you think if I study and write all the spare time I have that in the <choice><sic>corse</sic><corr>course</corr></choice> of two or three years I would be able to be an editor? I have been thinking for about two months that I would like to be something, and I <gap reason="damage" extent="5 or 6 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> that than <gap reason="damage" extent="6 words" quantity="20" unit="chars"/> <choice><sic>tryed</sic><corr>tried</corr></choice> to <gap reason="damage" extent="7 words" quantity="25" unit="chars"/> it, <gap reason="damage" extent="7 or 8 words" quantity="25" unit="chars"/> my <gap reason="damage" extent="2 lines" quantity="50" unit="chars"/> time <gap reason="damage" extent="7 or 8 words" quantity="25" unit="chars"/> only of <gap reason="damage" extent="5 or 6 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> you to think <gap reason="damage" extent="3 words" quantity="10" unit="chars"/> what I have said and tell me what conclusion you have come to <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#nhg">when</unclear></p>
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf002r" facs="loc_vm.00185.jpg" type="recto"/>
           <p>I see you <gap reason="damage" extent="3 words" quantity="20" unit="chars"/> work <choice><sic>to-gather</sic><corr>together</corr></choice> <gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> have become settled, and our love sure (although we have had very many rough times <choice><sic>to-gather</sic><corr>together</corr></choice>) but we have stuck <choice><sic>too</sic><corr>to</corr></choice> each other so far, and we will until we die, I know.</p>
            
            <p>I was down to see <gap reason="damage" extent="2 words" quantity="12" unit="chars"/> Friday <gap reason="damage" extent="4 or 5 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> him, as <gap reason="damage" extent="6 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/>ined <gap reason="damage" extent="3 lines" quantity="75" unit="chars"/> would <gap reason="damage" extent="7 or 8 words" quantity="25" unit="chars"/> and I <gap reason="damage" extent="7 words" quantity="25" unit="chars"/> out finding <gap reason="damage" extent="5 or 6 words" quantity="25" unit="chars"/></p>
            
            <p>Mother<ptr target="n0817b"/> is very sick and has been ever since I came home, she
            
            <pb xml:id="leaf002v" facs="loc_vm.00186.jpg" type="verso"/>
           
           was taken sick that day I was up there. Father is well as usual: he was to market today with potatoes.</p>
            
            <p>We are having a fine rain to-night down here, it hasn't come too soon either things were <choice><sic>kneeding</sic><corr>needing</corr></choice> <gap reason="damage" extent="1 line" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> will make <gap reason="damage" extent="1 line" quantity="15" unit="chars"/></p>
            
            <p><gap reason="damage" extent="5 words" quantity="30" unit="chars"/> time <gap reason="damage" extent="3 lines" quantity="50" unit="chars"/> so <gap reason="damage" extent="1 line" quantity="25" unit="chars"/> me <gap reason="damage" extent="7 words" quantity="25" unit="chars"/> improve my <gap reason="damage" extent="5 words" quantity="15" unit="chars"/> more.</p>
            
            <p>Well I have to close as the paper is given out.</p>

            <closer>
                <salute>Your loving son,</salute>
                <signed>H.L. Stafford</signed>
            </closer>
            <postscript>
                <p>P.S. write soon and oblige yours.</p>
            </postscript>
